{"id":20683,"date":"2015-06-11T19:16:42","date_gmt":"2015-06-11T15:16:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=20683"},"modified":"2019-03-21T13:06:48","modified_gmt":"2019-03-21T09:06:48","slug":"hadith-on-funerals-the-prophets-beautiful-supplication-for-the-deceased","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/06\/11\/hadith-on-funerals-the-prophets-beautiful-supplication-for-the-deceased\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Funerals: The Prophet\u2019s beautiful supplication for the deceased"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Awf ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, performed the funeral prayer and I memorized his supplication, \u201c<strong>O Allah, forgive him, have mercy on him, make him well, and pardon him. Dignify his residence and make his resting place spacious. Cleanse him with water, snow, and ice. Purify him from sins just as a white garment is purified from dirt. Offer him a home better than his home, people better than his people, and a wife better than his wife. Admit him into Paradise and save him from the punishment of the grave and the Hellfire<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Awf said, \u201cThe Prophet continued supplicating\u00a0until I wished that I had been that dead person.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 963<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0641\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0634\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652